Sensitivity Analysis

library(mrgsolve)
library(MASS)

A model

mod <- mrgsolve:::house() %>% Req(CP,RESP)

Sensitivity analysis on random values log Mean

mu <- log(as.numeric(param(mod))[s(CL,VC,KA)])
mu
.        CL        VC        KA 
. 0.0000000 2.9957323 0.1823216

Variance

Sigma <- diag(rep(0.2,length(mu)))

Sigma
.      [,1] [,2] [,3]
. [1,]  0.2  0.0  0.0
. [2,]  0.0  0.2  0.0
. [3,]  0.0  0.0  0.2

Simulate log-normal parameters

set.seed(111)
pars <- exp(mvrnorm(100, mu, Sigma)) %>% as.data.frame

head(pars)

Simulate

mod %>%
  ev(amt=1000) %>%
  idata_set(pars) %>%
  mrgsim(end=48,delta=0.1) %>%
  plot
